data.description: This is a UNIQUE OPPORTUNITY'EUR This property is an established income producing property on Air B&B. COMPLETELY UPDATED and a full IN-LAW SUITE!! Brand NEW ROOF and GUTTERS in 2022 by Lounsberry Roofing. 4 bedrooms, 3 full baths, 1 half bath, generator, multiple sheds, covered front porch with easy cleaning lvp floors, back deck, covered patio, artful trails. LUXURIATE in the park-like setting with total wooded privacy, ARTFUL TRAILS, landscape, hardscape and waterfall. Move-in ready with BRAND NEW gorgeous kitchen, beautiful gray cabinets, granite counters, gas cooking, stainless steel appliances. MORE UPDATES include French doors with built-in blinds that lead to the back deck, new flooring thru-out the main level, cozy wood-burning FIREPLACE. Master suite is complete with VAULTED ceiling, walk-in closet, double vanity, jetted tub, linen closet & detached shower. Nice size guest bedrooms, large laundry room with new flooring, rough-ed full bathroom, storage, outside entrance, wash basin, newer washer and dryer. Plus two HVAC systems. CONVENIENTLY located in the outside section with no gates. MUST SEE!!
